data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE DROP! This charming 3 bedroom home, sitting on an extra large lot in Deltona is a must see!  Perfect starter home or investment property. The open floor plan of this home with cozy living room and dining room is perfect for entertaining guests.  Kitchen was recently updated and features granite countertops and all stainless steel appliances that are only 3 years old.  From the dining room you can walk out to the outdoor patio perfect for grilling and enjoying the large fenced in, private back yard.  The garage was turned into a third bedroom with closet space. There is also a large laundry room with extra space for storage.  This home has no carpet. There is also NO HOA!  Conveniently located to restaurants, grocery stores and parks. Located less than 35 minutes to New Smyrna Beach and only 40 minutes to downtown Orlando. Schedule your showing today!
